<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū shì wǒ rén shēng de fāng xiàng wǒ yào yǔ tā tóng yuǎn háng,
 yé sū shì nǐ rén shēng fāng xiàng nǐ yào yǔ tā tóng yuǎn háng,
 bù pà shān gāo liú shuǐ zhǎng tā shì wǒ men de bǎo zhàng,
 yòu shì pǔ tiān xià de zhěng jiù quán rén lèi de xī wàng
 yé sū zhēn guāng chú zuì è, qù kǔn bǎng
 yé sū zhēn guāng quán rén lèi de xī wàng.</lyrics>
